<p>Independent agents cannot compete with GEICO and State Farm on head terms. Those companies spend hundreds of millions on brand SEO. But local and long-tail terms are wide open. A solo agent in Denver can rank #1 for "independent insurance agent Denver" with consistent local SEO.</p>
